title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1989-06-19
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger-> Franklin's Tower-> Walkin' Blues, Candyman, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, When Push Comes To Shove, Memphis Blues, Bird Song

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Playin' In The Band-> Crazy Fingers> Playin in the Band'> Drums> Space> I Will Take You Home> Watchtower> Black Peter> Throwing Stones> Not Fade Away, E: Knockin' on Heaven's Door
